## 🔧 **MCP SERVER CONFIGURATION**

### **MCP Memory Service Setup**

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "memory-service": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@doobidoo/mcp-memory-service"],
      "env": {
        "CHROMADB_HOST": "localhost",
        "CHROMADB_PORT": "8000",
        "MEMORY_DB_PATH": "./memory-bank"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### **Basic Memory Setup**

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "basic-memory": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@basicmachines-co/basic-memory"],
      "env": {
        "MEMORY_PATH": "./memory",
        "OBSIDIAN_VAULT": "./obsidian-vault"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

