## 🎯 **MEMORY BANK COMMANDS FOR 3-MODE SYSTEM**

### **Universal Memory Commands**

```bash
# Store memories
🧠 "store [category] [content]" → Store memory in appropriate category
🧠 "search [query]" → Search memories semantically
🧠 "retrieve [id]" → Retrieve specific memory by ID
